@node bugs
@title "Bugs"

 @{b}Known bugs:@{ub}

   o amigaguide.library from Workbench 3.1 (V40) @{b}crashes@{ub} on several occasions (click
     on the line below and you know what I mean ...)

===============================================================================

     Solution: Use @{"PowerGuide" link "powerguide"} or get an older amigaguide.library, e.g. the one
     from Workbench 3.0 (V39)

   o @{"PowerGuide" link "powerguide"} 1.20 (directly from Aminet CD 14 @{b}crashes@{ub} on textfiles with tabs,
     thus you should immediately upgrade to 1.21 (get the patch on Aminet)

 If you should find any additional bugs, enforcer hits or if you have any
 suggestions please @{"contact me" link "contact"}.

@endnode

