@node powerguide
@title "PowerGuide"

 PowerGuide  is  a  new AmigaGuide-viewer, which seems to be @{b}a lot faster@{ub}
 and  more reliable than amigaguide.library V39 or V40 by Commodore/Amiga
 Technologies,  though  still  having  a  couple of bugs or unimplemented
 features (Guideance just fixes the missing XPK-support).

 I   found   the   executable   (without   any  docs)  on  Aminet  CD  14
 (AMINET14:Tools/PowerGuide).  I  recommend  you to @{b}patch@{ub} this executable
 (1.20)  to  version 1.21 to avoid any @{b}crashes@{ub}. You can find the patch on
 Aminet.

 PowerGuide  is  Copyright  (C)  1995-1996  Stefan Ossowskis Schatztruhe,
 Gesellschaft f³r Software mbH. Written by Matthias Scheler.

@endnode
